<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>404 - 페이지를 찾을 수 없음</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f8f9fa; /* Light gray background */
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh; /* Ensure it takes full viewport height */
      margin: 0;
    }

    .error-card {
      border: none;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 0.5rem 1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Subtle shadow */
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .error-image-block {
      /* If you add an image, you might want to style its container */
      max-width: 200px; /* Example size for an image */
      margin: 0 auto 1.5rem auto; /* Center image and add some bottom margin */
    }

    .error-image-block img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem; /* Larger heading for impact */
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #007bff; /* Bootstrap primary blue */
      border-color: #007bff;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3; /* Darker blue on hover */
      border-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main class="maintenance-block">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6">
          <div class="card error-card mt-5">
            <div class="card-body text-center">
              <div class="error-image-block mb-4">
                </div>
              <h1 class="text-danger fw-bold">404 - 페이지를 찾을 수 없음</h1>
              <p class="text-muted mt-3 mb-4">
                요청하신 페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다.<br />
                주소를 다시 확인하거나, 홈으로 돌아가 주세요.
              </p>
              <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">홈으로 돌아가기</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>